{"compress":true,"commitItems":[["ea68e7c1-aa4a-4583-b8cd-c8836cf21eca",1528595852442,"",[[1528595794620,["Administrator@Tielemao",[[1,0,"### 安装express\n\n```\nnpm install -g express \n```\n\n### 安装express命令工具\n\n```\nnpm install -g express-generator\n```\n\n### 查看express命令\n\n```\nexpress -h\n```\n\n![](http://i.imgur.com/mkJIbzf.png)\n\n### 创建初始项目\n\n创建默认初始化项目是，其视图使用的是jade模板引擎\n\n```\nexpress 项目名\n```\n\n创建ejs模板引擎项目\n\n```\nexpress -e 项目名\n```\n\n### 下载相关的模组\n\n进入项目目录，执行下面的命令\n\n```\nnpm install\n```\n\n![](http://i.imgur.com/EKPfx54.png)\n\n### 项目结构说明\n\n![](http://i.imgur.com/5EqKtJI.png)\n1\\. 【bin】存放启动项目的脚本文件\n2\\. 【node_modules】 存放所有的项目依赖库\n3\\. 【public】静态文件(css,js,img)\n4\\. 【routes】路由文件(MVC中的C,controller)\n5\\. 【views】页面文件(Ejs模板)\n6\\. 【app.js】是项目的入口，设置项目的模板引擎类型，报错页面，端口设置等\n7\\. 【package.json】项目依赖配置及开发者信息\n\n### 启动\n\n项目目录下执行\n\n```\nnpm start\n```\n\n![](http://i.imgur.com/MGaq0oX.png)\n\n### 查看\n\n默认查看地址：[http://127.0.0.1:3000/](http://127.0.0.1:3000/)\n![](http://i.imgur.com/8PEdyZe.png)"]],[0,0],[801,801]]],[1528596157928,["Administrator@Tielemao",[[-1,331,"![](http://i.imgur.com/EKPfx54.png)"]],[331,366],[331,331]]],[1528596158514,["Administrator@Tielemao",[[-1,332,"\n"]],[331,331],[330,330]]],[1528596159008,["Administrator@Tielemao",[[-1,331,"\n"]],[330,330],[329,329]]],[1528596159653,["Administrator@Tielemao",[[-1,328,"`"]],[329,329],[328,328]]],[1528596161602,["Administrator@Tielemao",[[1,328,"`"]],[328,328],[329,329]]],[1528596168417,["Administrator@Tielemao",[[-1,146,"![](http://i.imgur.com/mkJIbzf.png)"]],[146,181],[146,146]]],[1528596177258,["Administrator@Tielemao",[[1,147,"![express-h]($res/express-h.jpg)\n\n"]],[146,146],[180,180]]],[1528596179670,["Administrator@Tielemao",[[-1,146,"\n"]],[146,146],[145,145]]],[1528596180236,["Administrator@Tielemao",[[-1,145,"\n"]],[145,145],[144,144]]],[1528596218879,["Administrator@Tielemao",[[-1,340,"![](http://i.imgur.com/5EqKtJI.png)"]],[340,375],[340,340]]],[1528596305704,["Administrator@Tielemao",[[1,